I have owned and operated a pedicab  
company in Portland Oregon since March 22, 2007. We operate unber the name
 
Pdx Pedicab (PDX) being the Portland Airport code and a common
abbreviation  
for Portland. In addition I purchased the following domains on March 22,  
2007:
PdxPediab.com
Pdx Pedicabs.com
PortlandPedicab.com, and PortlandPedicabs.com

The company listed as Portland Pedicab and Portland Pedicabs both violate 

my rights to those names. The company listed there actually operates as  
Portland Pedal Works and Portland Cascadia Pedicabs and a host of other  
names none associated with their legal business name.
